and John refused to write anything.

08:35.141 --> 08:38.345
Because all such people take charge.

08:38.575 --> 08:40.450
They become in charge.

08:40.633 --> 08:47.768
They think they are responsible for it,
while they are not at all capable.

08:47.893 --> 08:51.683
