09:29.920 --> 09:36.671
I was also born in a Christian family and
I was shocked the way they interpreted

09:37.282 --> 09:42.527
Christ's life and the way talked about it with great authority.

09:43.575 --> 09:45.525
Books and books were written.

09:46.026 --> 09:48.335
