10:15.467 --> 10:22.172
They all wanted to have power; they wanted to have power in religion.

10:24.126 --> 10:31.078
The power in religion is inside, and that should be awakened.

10:31.658 --> 10:38.159
I must say thanks to the Sufis of this country and other countries

10:38.265 --> 10:46.685
