and so many of them were killed.

11:09.245 --> 11:21.551
This is happening even today; I find that
people don't want to listen to reality, to the truth.

11:22.321 --> 11:25.749
But I was so happy yesterday, really overjoyed,

11:25.884 --> 11:33.845
to see that even the people who were Muslims, were Islamic,

11:33.988 --> 11:46.292
