25:05.457 --> 25:09.652
out of our reading, whatever it is,

25:09.771 --> 25:15.596
whatever we had developed, we were having - just drops out.

25:16.718 --> 25:23.217
When the Kundalini rises and you become one with the Divine,

25:23.321 --> 25:27.257
