27:01.002 --> 27:08.453
you can become a different person, a reformed person

27:08.540 --> 27:14.235
and a great spiritual person.
You can become; it means that.

27:14.290 --> 27:16.555
Why do we give eggs?

27:16.608 --> 27:18.618
People don't know.

27:18.769 --> 27:20.789
I asked so many people.

27:20.836 --> 27:25.763
I asked even some priests who think
they are great authorities of Christianity.

27:26.010 --> 27:30.095
They didn't know why they give eggs.

27:30.705 --> 27:42.320
Secondly, if you read the story about
the birth of Shri Ganesh

27:42.484 --> 27:50.251
and then you proceed on, you’ll be surprised is written down
that it was called as Brahmand -

27:50.530 --> 27:58.576
means the egg of the Brahma that came into existence,

27:58.942 --> 28:06.857
and half of it became the Mahavishnu means the Christ,

28:06.960 --> 28:13.380
and half of it remained as Shri Ganesh.

28:13.721 --> 28:23.540
